---
title: Chicken-Tofu Stir Fry & Coconut Sauce with Soy Veggies, Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: Our tofu is cooked to crispy perfection in our curry powder. Then, we've teamed it with a dazzling coconut sauce made using Bengal curry paste, plus steamed rice flavoured with fragrant garlic. When you serve this up, everyone will be singing you praises!
